items.title: Carol Burnett will bring ‘An Evening of Laughter’ to Comerica Theatre
items.summary:
Carol Burnett, award-winning actress and best-selling author, will is coming to Phoenix on Sunday, December 17 to perform “An Evening of Laughter and Reflection” at Comerica Theatre. Tickets go on sale to the public starting Friday, September 15th at 10 a.m. at Ticketmaster.com, the box office or by phone at 1.800.745.3000.
